"Do you hear me? Get off this island at once! Clear out, and be quick about it!"\par
The stranger glared at them angrily. Frank eaw that nothing would be gained by arguing the matter. He shrugged.\par
"All right, sir."\par
"Thanks for the hospitality!" sang out Chet, as the boys turned about and retraced their steps down the path.\par
